Package: data.QC
Title: Quality control of hydrometeorological data
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonnathan", "Landi", , "jonnathan.landi@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-3162-6647"))
Description: data.QC is an algorithm designed to perform robust preprocessing of meteorological data. It provides functionalities for cleaning, quality control, and analysis of hydrometeorological datasets.
